Job Description
A leading Group of Companies requires following staff for its Pharmaceutical manufacturer concerned based at Lahore at attractive package.
Manager Accounts (C.A Final)
We are looking for a dedicated person who has just completed his C.A or about to complete and must have strong Managerial skills & ability to handle computerized accounting system and must have good Administrative, Communication and Computer skills.
Note: Short listed candidates shall be called for interview and no TA/DA shall be admissible.Apply Instructions for This Job
